{"tid":1502469,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我地需要改變唔好再諗住不受傷，不流血，不被捕","createTime":"2019-08-24T16:27:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T14:11:43.000Z","uid":68982,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"63a43c0ebe70ab3b46191fd18e89810d2a134a3e","tid":1502469,"uid":68982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:27:30.000Z","msg":"如果我地繼續抱住呢個心態出去，速龍衝出黎捉，大家只會一味向後跑。<br />\n<br />\n今日係九龍灣個陣速龍一出大家就亂哂咁跑。但大家跑緊既時候知唔知，後面有手足跌低，有人比狗捉。大家淨係諗住不受傷，不流血，不被捕，但個一波就有二十幾個手足被捕，有手足受傷甚至爆眼。<br />\n<br />\n我地咁樣已經唔係齊上齊落，我唔想每一次都要喊住返屋企，我地既安全係被捕、受傷既手足換返黎架。我地所有手足係同為一體，任何一位手足有事，都等於自己有事。<br />\n<br />\n我地要做既有咩事都要一齊頂，受傷就一齊受傷，流血就一齊流血，被捕就一齊被捕。我意思唔係要大家去送頭，係要顧及其他手足，姐係要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">救人</span></strong>呀。你自己受傷流血你都識得去救去止血，記住所有手足都係自己一部分而唔係condom，手足受傷、被捕唔係向後跑，係救人呀。<br />\n<br />\n如果我地改變唔到，我真係建議唔好玩陣地，速龍一衝，但又企太密，有事就向後亂跑，有手足撞跌，成日差啲人踩人。雖然今日有還擊到，但啲手足已經捉左，我地救唔到人呀。<br />\n<br />\n就算我地未準備好衝，但我地一定要有救人既準備。少一個手足就等於自斷手臂。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n題外話，有人影相就由佢，我地屌極到有人會影，不如直接右手遮眼、左手斷指等佢影，對住佢講還眼，好過屌鳩佢。同埋一屌好易牽動佢地手足既情緒。"},{"pid":"c8a6ee1bc34b476d4b8dd85776d28556e04e0172","tid":1502469,"uid":68982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:35:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4161dd8eb6ea315422a4c940f08bed52a7503174","tid":1502469,"uid":68982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:39:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7fbad561d1d6f7fb5e7f1435fb7fc84357dc9ebe","tid":1502469,"uid":68982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:41:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"67418a42aca82a127e04dff2a4b2cc337c992739","tid":1502469,"uid":68982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:41:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"303ea787ca558ceac2e3ce8d66398b7a86f3c920","tid":1502469,"uid":68982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:43:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"db67177cf01fee6370bdcbade95be0d43c22a250","tid":1502469,"uid":68982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:49:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0c7789230cd1deae73bf99f065991873fd719b95","tid":1502469,"uid":68982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:00:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"457e5a4d5c05f5c3e85505eeaf43e63931ccb2c9","tid":1502469,"uid":68982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:01:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2fd73d3df72d52593a8019aa64b4f8798ea0e843","tid":1502469,"uid":283972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:13:34.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c15c8f675d67c83f62524d148f5774809e01d7d","tid":1502469,"uid":283972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:14:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d81e1e113bb2c0353264a8ad002098401344bf64","tid":1502469,"uid":68982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T20:08:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e38d8c485d44729926d0089698f244c569dd82b4","tid":1502469,"uid":68982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T08:21:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"87d8287d6e8ce659a0a4e8f6b11c81f2f8ac9314","tid":1502469,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T08:25:34.000Z","msg":"不受傷，不流血，不被捕 <br />\n對抗爭者黎講根本就係個童話"},{"pid":"a46985737788580005d9beddfe636843530d0cb9","tid":1502469,"uid":68982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:18:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8e3a93c9f326491f5aef2bba4a8970265044d84f","tid":1502469,"uid":68982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:31:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f82ec9f7ee218ec87dfe7475dba25ace682a5fce","tid":1502469,"uid":68982,"like":0